import { Tabs, Tab, Toolbar, Typography, Button } from '@mui/material';
import AppBar from '@mui/material/AppBar';

export const Navbar = () => {



    return (
        <>
            <AppBar elevation={0}>
                <Toolbar disableGutters sx={{ p: 3, ml: 5 }} >
                    <Tabs >
                        <Tab >
                            <Typography>
                                Logo
                            </Typography>
                        </Tab>
                        <Tab label='HOME' />
                        <Tab label='What is GPT?' />
                        <Tab label='OPEN AI' />
                        <Tab label='CASE STUDIES' />
                        <Tab label='Library' />

                    </Tabs>
                    <Button 
                    size={'large'}
                    sx={{marginLeft:'auto',marginRight:'20px'}}
                    color='success'
                    disableElevation
                    variant='outlined'>
                        Sign In
                    </Button>
                    <Button
                    sx={{marginRight:'50px'}}
                    color='success'
                    disableElevation
                    variant='contained'>
                        Sign Up
                    </Button>


                </Toolbar>

            </AppBar>
        </>
    )
}
